287
00:14:12,994 --> 00:14:16,594
with one of the problems he listed,
because cerebrovascular diseases

288
00:14:16,754 --> 00:14:19,474
are the fifth-leading cause
of death in the United States.

289
00:14:19,634 --> 00:14:21,874
