00:19:56,084 --> 00:19:58,644
and Matt Lauer was the one
who went home and cried,

405
00:19:58,804 --> 00:20:00,284
and, look, look,

406
00:20:00,444 --> 00:20:01,804
you can see

407
00:20:01,964 --> 00:20:04,724
why people are vulnerable
to psychics.

408
00:20:04,884 --> 00:20:08,324
A message from a lost loved one
is something many grieving people

409
00:20:08,484 --> 00:20:11,604
would do anything for,
and psychics may tell themselves

410
00:20:11,764 --> 00:20:14,084
that they offer a harmless way
to deal with loss.

411
00:20:14,244 --> 00:20:17,365
Just watch as Theresa Caputo
pretty much spells that out

412
00:20:17,525 --> 00:20:19,685
in response
to a fairly obvious question.

413
00:20:19,845 --> 00:20:23,005
So when a tragedy happens--
let's say a murder.

414
00:20:23,165 --> 00:20:25,485
- Yeah.
- If somebody comes to a loved one

415
00:20:25,645 --> 00:20:30,085
and the spirit of the person
who was murdered is there,

416
00:20:30,245 --> 00:20:33,245
