00:22:12,408 --> 00:22:14,768
<i>from so-called psychic detectives.</i>

450
00:22:14,928 --> 00:22:17,768
<i>They say some even showed up</i>
<i>at their front door,</i>

451
00:22:17,928 --> 00:22:21,448
